1768015472^(connect) - RESPECT THE NETWORK: Avoid excessive traffic or spamming the node to ensure smooth operation for all users.%0D
1768015472^(connect) - SHARE RESPONSIBLY: Only post accurate and relevant DX spots to maintain the quality of the service.%0D
1768015472^(connect) - BE CONSIDERATE: This node is a shared resource. Let%E2%80%99s work together to keep it accessible and reliable for everyone.%0D
